>>>>>>>>>>
step to run mongodb 
<<<<<<<<<<<< <<

// Mongo Server //   
> open first cmd 
> go inside the mongodb folder 
cd c:\program file\mongodb\server\4.4\bin 
> mongod.exe  
(Above step will start mongo server on port 27017)

//// to Start mongo console /////
> open second cmd   
> go inside the mongodb folder 
cd c:\program file\mongodb\server\4.4\bin 
> mongo.exe       

